room_title: Escape room "Jailbreak" by Escape the Cape in Fort Myers
room_address: 728 SW Pine Island Rd #16 Cape Coral, FL 33991
room_description:
You and a group of your wildest friends had a little too much fun out on the town last night.  Luckily for you guys, the guard on duty has dozed off and left the keys just out of arms reach. Can you and your friends use all of your resources in sixty minutes to get the keys and break out without waking up the guard?
Please note that you will be handcuffed.
